- All small objects of any color other than green are labeled 'True' regardless of their shape.
- All triangles of any color other than green and size other than small are labeled 'True'.
- Large blue shapes (other than triangles) and medium blue shapes of any kind are labeled 'False'.

Applying this rule to Group 25:
-small green circle -> True (because it is green)
-small yellow triangle -> True (because it is small)
-large yellow triangle -> True (because it is a large triangle that isn't green)
-large blue circle -> False (because it is a large blue shape that isn't a triangle)
